fields.name: lkp_PREVIOUS_VIN_NOT_NULL
fields.expression:
---IIF(RCRD_IN='C' AND length ( PRVS_VIN_ID) !=0,:LKP.lkp_FNC_CNTRCT_FC(PRVS_VIN_ID,PRVS_ACNT_NB))

---orginal IIF(RCRD_IN='C' AND NOT  ISNULL(PRVS_VIN_ID)  ,:LKP.lkp_FNC_CNTRCT_FC(PRVS_VIN_ID,PRVS_ACNT_NB))
---IIF(RCRD_IN='C' AND NOT  ISNULL(PRVS_VIN_ID)  ,:LKP.lkp_FNC_CNTRCT_PRE_NULL(PRVS_ACNT_NB))

IIF(RCRD_IN='C' AND NOT  ISNULL(PRVS_VIN_ID)  ,:LKP.lkp_FNC_CNTRCT_FC(PRVS_VIN_ID,PRVS_ACNT_NB))

fields.name: CHECK1
fields.expression:
---IIF(NOT  ISNULL(PRVS_VIN_ID)AND RCRD_IN='C'   ,:LKP.lkp_FNC_CNTRCT_PRE_NULL.(PRVS_ACNT_NB))

IIF(RCRD_IN='C' AND NOT  ISNULL(PRVS_VIN_ID)  ,:LKP.lkp_FNC_CNTRCT_PRE_NULL(PRVS_ACNT_NB))

fields.name: PREVIOUS_VIN_NOT_NULL_FLAG_RCRD
fields.expression:
IIF(RCRD_IN='C' AND NOT ISNULL(lkp_PREVIOUS_VIN_NOT_NULL) AND
PREVIOUS_VIN_NOT_NULL_FLAG='Y'
,'Y','N')

fields.name: PREVIOUS_VIN_NULL_FLAG_RCRD
fields.expression:
IIF(RCRD_IN='C' AND NOT ISNULL(lkp_PREVIOUS_VIN_NULL) AND
PREVIOUS_VIN_NULL_FLAG='Y' , 'Y','N')

fields.name: ERR_RECORD_FLAG
fields.expression:
---IIF(RCRD_IN='C' AND   (ISNULL(lkp_PREVIOUS_VIN_NULL)   OR 
---ISNULL(lkp_PREVIOUS_VIN_NOT_NULL))   
---'Y','N')

IIF( RCRD_IN='C'  AND
(
 (ISNULL(lkp_PREVIOUS_VIN_NULL)  AND PREVIOUS_VIN_NULL_FLAG='Y')
OR
(PREVIOUS_VIN_NOT_NULL_FLAG='Y'  AND ISNULL(lkp_PREVIOUS_VIN_NOT_NULL))
)

,'Y','N')
